<P><A NAME="Figure5.1"></A><CITE><I>FIGURE 5.1: RADIOACTIVE DECAY OF
DISPOSAL - INVENTORY WITH TIME</I></CITE><BR>(Click on image to see in full
size)</P>
<P><A HREF="images/pe1551.jpg"><IMG
