IMPACT OF HURRICANE LUIS, SANITATION SITUATION OF PERSONS
EVACUATED TO NORTHERN PART OF ISLAND FOLLOWING VOLCANIC
ACTIVITIES, HADALREADY CREATED HEALTH PROBLEMS THAT ARE LIKELY
TO BECOME MORE SERIOUS IN AFTERMATH OF HURRICANE.

