From: Emergency Information Administrator <incident@lan.vita.org>
Subject: Caribbean: Hurricane  DHA-03



                    CARIBBEAN-HURRICANE LUIS
           ANTIGUA AND BARBUDA, NETHERLANDS ANTILLES,
                       ST. KITTS AND NEVIS
                   DHA SITUATION REPORT NO. 3
                         8 SEPTEMBER 1995

ST KITTS AND NEVIS
------------------
1. GOVT OF ST KITTS AND NEVIS HAS REQUESTED DHA TO LAUNCH AN
APPEAL FOR INTERNATIONAL ASSISTANCE.

2. IMMEDIATE NEEDS INCLUDE FOOD, SHELTER AND OTHER EQUIPMENT AND
