     SWEDEN              FINANCING ONE DHA-UNDAC EXPERT

     SWITZERLAND         USD 100,000 THROUGH DHA (ESTABLISHMENT
                         OF ON-SITE RELIEF COORDINATION CELL
                         IN PYONGYANG)

     UNITED STATES       USD 25,000

     OTHERS:

     IFRC                USD 50,000 DISASTER RELIEF EMERGENCY
                         FUND

     MSF                 USD 1,000,000 WORTH OF MEDICAL EQUIPMENT
                         AND ASSESSMENT TEAM

     NIPPON FOUNDATION   USD 20,000 (THROUGH DHA)
     (FORMERLY SASAKAWA FOUNDATION)

     AMERICAN FIELDS     USD 10,000
     SERVICE COMMITTEE

     CHURCH OF JESUS     80,000 LBS OF WINTER CLOTHING (THROUGH
     CHRIST OF LATTER    DHA), 35,000 LBS POWDERED MILK, AND
     DAY SAINTS          MEDICINES  VALUED AT USD 166,000


