<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>About TLS Page</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="tlsslogo.gif" WIDTH="225" HEIGHT="55" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><p></center><font size=+2>Travel Leader PR News</font><br>This is a service provided by travel suppliers primarily for the use of travel writers and editors. There will be, however, bonus traffic from the travel industry and consumers alike. New releases are featured in "What's New" for one month, and can remain in the database indefinitely.  Members of the press are made aware of this p.r. service through direct mail promotion to them by Travel Marketing Services . <p>Billing will be according to pages online the last business day of of each month, and will be based upon the rates specified in the <a href="fact.htm">Fact Sheet</a>. <hr><font size=+2>The Newsletters</font><br>The Travel Market Leader, an industry newsletter, discusses issues and trends. Publishes a calendar of meetings of interest to industry marketing and management executives. Also an update on key shifts in responsibilities, be they people, advertising or public relations agencies.<p>The Travel Leader, a consumer newsletter, has information and ideas for travelers. Discusses services to travelers they might not otherwise know about. Likewise, noteworthy developments at destinations and resorts; on the various transportation modes;  unusual cruises and tours; ways to save money; etc. <p>Display advertising is available in both letters. Contact Travel Leader Services at 203 655-4947 for details.<p><a href="http://www.travelleader.com/butbar2.map"><IMG SRC="http://www.travelleader.com/tlsbutbr.gif" ISMAP border=0 WIDTH="390" HEIGHT="78" ALIGN=bottom></a></UL><P><CENTER></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
