<html><head><title>About Travel Leader Services</title></head><body bgcolor="ffffff"><font size=+1>Please send all press releases, backgrounds, etc. in the following format:<ul><li>single-spaced<li>12 point New York or Times New Roman font<li>Left-justified (no centering)<li>No accents above letters<li>Text Only documents - </font>All word processing applications are able to save documents as basic ASCII-text. Simply select "Save As..." under the "File" menu and choose "Text Only" as the file format.<p><font size=+1>Releases should be e-mailed to <a href="mailto:dnesbett@travelleasder.com">dnesbett@travelleasder.com</a>. They may be placed within the e-mail text itself, or sent as attached files.<p>When converted into HTML for placement on our site, all subject headers, lists and so forth will be formatted accordingly (centering, bold-face, etc.)</font><p><center><a href="http://www.travelleader.com/butbar2.map"><IMG SRC="http://www.travelleader.com/tlsbutbr.gif" ISMAP border=0 WIDTH="390" HEIGHT="78" ALIGN=bottom></a></center></body></html>
