<html><head><title>Inter-Continental TOC</title></head><body bgcolor="ffffff"><center><img src="belgian2.gif" border=0></center<p><a href="comics.html">100th Anniversary of Comic Strip Art - A year long event</a><p><a href="ensdelv.html">"From Ensor to Delvaux" major exhibit to be held at the provincial Museum of Modern Art in Ostend from October 5, 1996 until February 2, 1997</a><p><center><a href="http://www.travelleader.com/butbar2.map"><IMG SRC="http://www.travelleader.com/tlsbutbr.gif" ISMAP border=0 WIDTH="390" HEIGHT="78" ALIGN=bottom></a></center></body></html>
